Generating the documentation:

Install BigJob from sources, i.e., in BigJob source root::

    virtualenv /tmp/BJ/
    source /tmp/BJ/bin/activate
    easy_install .

Next install Sphinx in the virtualenv::

    pip install sphinx

Change to the docs directory.

    * make html creates the HTML documentation in build/html
    * make latexpdf creates the PDF manual in build/latex






